{"tid":2304962,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG] Bot game 狼人Avalon仲有...","createTime":"2020-11-29T08:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T15:11:58.000Z","uid":46843,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8596325fc776ad2d4134953dc73291841a94cb49","tid":2304962,"uid":46843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"呢個谷玩好多bot game <br />\n狼人 Avalon 牛牛 Dixit 食字都有<br />\n如果無嘅話 你同admin 講 佢地會即刻加比你<br />\n仲會有班廢青冗員無game開就吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span class=\"large\">歡迎任何巴絲入谷 唔理男女平衡呢啲野啦</span></em></strong> <br />\n<br />\n雖然無特別注重男女平衡 但係而家個谷好似女多過男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋入面既人都好friendly 唔識玩可以問<br />\n絕無小圈子<br />\n <strong><em><span class=\"large\">只要你出聲好多人都會應你機</span></em></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家個谷唔係成日開到game 靠新入谷既大家撐起個谷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/jC164Ziu5qaj6jxb6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FjC164Ziu5qaj6jxb6&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=d093156d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/jC164Ziu5qaj6jxb6</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣就簡單填張form 留個ID<br />\nTelegram見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span class=\"large\">想快啲入谷既 privacy 既groups and channel 較返everyone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></em></strong>"},{"pid":"0e76325de938ca8cdc69c5c791d9cf9cfbfa8c71","tid":2304962,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T09:15:41.000Z","msg":"有靚女先入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7541ce3bc69e1b56722f0be1bcfcde1a1304653","tid":2304962,"uid":46843,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhhhhhhhhsup"},{"pid":"30670a223d2c